Opt out: ['Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) you have the right to opt-out of the sale of your personal information and the sharing of your personal information to third parties for cross-context behavioral advertsing. Other state privacy laws similar to the CCPA allow individuals similar rights. These cookies collect information for analytics and to personalize your experience with targeted ads. You may exercise your right to opt out of the sale of personal information by using this toggle switch. If you opt out we will not be able to offer you personalised ads and will not hand over your personal information to any third parties. If you have enabled privacy controls on your browser (such as a plugin), we have to take that as a valid request to opt-out. Therefore we would not be able to track your activity through the web. This may affect our ability to personalize ads according to your preferences.']

['Your Privacy Choices', 'Under certain state laws in the United States, “sale” or “sharing” of personal information is defined broadly and in a way that may include allowing third parties to receive certain information for certain functions, including but not limited to interest-based advertising. To opt out of the sale or sharing of your personal information relating to cookies, move the toggle to the left and select "Confirm My Choice". If you choose to opt out of this data sharing, you will still see ads, though they may be less relevant to you. These ads may be based on historical information or information shared or sold by other sources. You will need to renew this choice each time you clear your cookies or use a new browser or device. This opt-out applies only to certain cookie (“online”) data we have about you. Opt out:
['As described above, under the California Consumer Privacy Act, you have the right to opt-out of the “sale” of your personal information to third parties. These cookies collect information primarily for analytics and to personalize your experience with targeted ads. You may exercise your right to opt out of the sale of personal information by using this toggle switch or by pressing the "Do Not Sell" button below.  This may affect our ability to personalize ads according to your preferences.', 'When you visit our website, we store cookies on your browser to collect information. The information collected might relate to you, your preferences or your device, and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to and to provide a more personalized web experience. 

Under the California Consumer Privacy Act of 2018 ("CCPA"), California residents have the right to opt out of the "sale" of personal information (transfers or disclosures to other businesses or third parties for monetary or other valuable consideration) we collect about them ("Personal Data") as described in our Privacy & Cookies Policy.  You can find our Privacy & Cookies Policy by clicking on the link below.

We value your privacy and want to honor your preferences regarding your data. Guidelines from the State of California setting forth exactly how companies are required to comply with CCPA are still being developed, and we will monitor those developments carefully. Set forth below are options for California residents who want to opt-out of certain transfers of data that we may have collected from you as you have interacted with our website, our apps, or otherwise used our services. We may update this information as guidance from the State of California is clarified and finalized.

Generally, transfers of data occur (1) because of cookies and similar technologies on your desktop browser or your mobile device, or (2) from our systems.  To exercise your choice with respect to cookies or other technologies, please use the button below.  To let us know about your choices with respect to other transfers, please submit a DSAR request using the link below. 
                        ']
